channel.title: Looking for someone to help put server online! (Without No-IP)
channel.description:

Who ever can help me put my server online another way, will be co owner of my awesome server, and get rep. Thanks...
P.S. Already tried resetting my password, etc. I made a new account also still doesn't work.
